# Filter App Project 

<details>
  <summary> About this project</summary>

This is a full-stack app where users can:
- Upload images
- Apply filters
- Save results

</details>

<details>
  <summary>⚙️ Tech stack</summary>

- TypeScript
- Node.js + Express
- PostgreSQL (Drizzle ORM)
- React frontend

</details>

<details>
  <summary> How to run</summary>

1. Install dependencies
2. Run server
3. Open app in browser

</details>
